es &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; am &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; tag ( english : it happened in broad daylight ) is a 1958 &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; suspense film directed by ladislao vajda . in 1997 , it was remade under the same title as a german tv film , directed by nico &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . there was also a dutch remake of the film , by rudolf van den berg , under the title the cold light of day made in 1995 . the original screenplay was written by friedrich dürrenmatt , a swiss playwright and novelist , and the first incarnation of the film is still acclaimed by critics . heinz rühmann and gert fröbe both starred in the 1958 movie .